com.iplanet.services.naming.share

Class NamingRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iplanet.services.naming.share.NamingRequest

  • public class NamingRequest
extends Object
    This NamingRequest class represents a NamingRequest XML document. The NamingRequest DTD is defined as the following: 

         <?xml version="1.0">
     < !DOCTYPE NamingRequest [
     < !ELEMENT NamingRequest (GetNamingProfile)>
     < !ATTLIST NamingRequest
       vers   CDATA #REQUIRED
       reqid  CDATA #REQUIRED
       sessid CDATA #REQUIRED>
     < !ELEMENT GetNamingProfile EMPTY>
     ]>
